                <note rend="inline" type="source">814.51/589: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Guatemala</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Geissler</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Guatemala</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1927-05-31T11:00:00-07:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 31, 1927—11 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received 3:10 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>51. The Assembly yesterday approved the railway debt settlement.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Geissler</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
